# Project Summary

# E-Commerce Sales Performance Dashboard

## Project Overview

This project was developed to analyze e-commerce sales performance using SQL and Power BI.

The objective of the project is to transform raw sales data into meaningful business insights through:
- data cleaning
- exploratory data analysis
- business analysis
- dashboard visualization

The final result is an interactive business intelligence dashboard designed to support data-driven decision making.

---

# Objectives

The project aims to:

- Analyze overall sales and profitability performance
- Identify top-performing product categories
- Understand regional sales distribution
- Monitor monthly sales trends
- Evaluate product-level performance
- Present insights using an executive-style dashboard

---

# Tools & Technologies

| Tools | Purpose |
|---|---|
| MySQL | Data cleaning and SQL analysis |
| Power BI | Dashboard development and visualization |
| DAX | KPI calculations and measures |
| Excel/CSV | Raw dataset source |

---

# Workflow

## 1. Data Collection

The dataset was imported from CSV format into MySQL for structured analysis.

---

## 2. Data Cleaning

Data cleaning steps included:
- renaming columns
- converting date formats
- checking null values
- validating numeric fields
- checking duplicate records

---

## 3. Exploratory Data Analysis

SQL queries were used to analyze:
- total sales
- total profit
- total orders
- category performance
- regional performance
- monthly trends

---

## 4. Dashboard Development

An interactive Power BI dashboard was developed containing:
- KPI cards
- monthly sales trend analysis
- category performance charts
- regional sales distribution
- top product analysis
- profitability analysis

---

# Dashboard Features

## KPI Monitoring
Tracks:
- Total Sales
- Total Profit
- Total Orders
- Total Quantity

## Trend Analysis
Visualizes monthly sales and profit trends over time.

## Category Analysis
Compares sales contribution by product category.

## Regional Analysis
Shows regional distribution of sales performance.

## Product Analysis
Highlights top-performing products based on revenue and profitability.

---

# Key Business Insights

- Electronics category generated the highest sales revenue.
- West region contributed the largest sales share.
- Profitability remained healthy across categories.
- Monthly sales trends revealed recurring seasonal patterns.

---

